title: Gigi Hadid shows-off vacationbikini bod before walking for NYFW
text:
Gigi Hadid shows-off 'vacation'bikini bod before walking for NYFW 
Technology Industry News.Net (ANI) : Sunday 30th August, 2015 
American model Gigi Hadid is making the most of her final vacation days as she took to Instagram to share her few bikini pictures before she takes the ramp for New York Fashion Week (NYFW). 
The 20-year -old model shared the picture of palm trees and sparkling blue water on Instagram and captioned, "My pre-fashion month vacay 
> 
missing this view already!," The People magazine reports. 
Shortly after her bikini post, she shared another post showing her securing the 'dock jump' in a two-piece.
